                <div class="col-lg-auto col-md-auto">
                    <h2>15 May 2019</h2>
                    <p><b>Ver 1.2 and Ver1.1J</b></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Adjusted the Sensitivity options based on player feedback</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h2>12 APRIL 2019</h2>
                    <p><b>Ver 1.1</b></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Created sensitivity option to let players select how much the game will smooth out the launch curve of the bowling ball.  Since different devices can have varying levels of sensitivity, this option can help players with more sensitive devices bowl straight.</li>
                        <li>High Score now accessible from main menu.</li>
                        <li>Logo will occasionally switch to Japanese language version to highlight the launch of the Japanese iteration of the game.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><b>Ver 1.0J</b></p>
                    <p>Japanese language version of Nice Bowling launched.  Includes text in menus, in-game effects, high score, and credits screens as well as Japanese language logos and graphics.</p>
                    <h2>13 MARCH 2019</h2>
                    <p>Nice Bowling ver 1.0 released on Android.  Media updated on website to reflect release artwork, game modes, and general aesthetic.</p>
                </div>
